Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Black  Rock  Shooter  卻無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:41.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向劃破黑暗的流星許願  再一次向前奔跑
