Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你想的那樣
