Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個世界會比活在這個世界更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優…
