Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要不要讓那個人承受一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份痛楚…
